he went straight into the room,

281
00:18:46,040 --> 00:18:46,900
found the body,

282
00:18:46,920 --> 00:18:48,380
and rushed out screaming.

283
00:18:48,440 --> 00:18:50,840
The night soil collector was curious and peeked inside.

284
00:18:50,840 --> 00:18:51,440
So,

285
00:18:51,480 --> 00:18:53,740
the time he went in and out was very short.

286
00:18:53,760 --> 00:18:55,720
He couldn't possibly have had time to commit the crime.

287
00:18:55,720 --> 00:18:57,120
Looking at it this way,

288
00:18:57,440 --> 00:19:00,040
it's highly likely he committed suicide.

289
00:19:01,960 --> 00:19:02,880
People like him

290
00:19:03,080 --> 00:19:04,080
deserve to die.

291
00:19:04,920 --> 00:19:05,680
What nonsense are you talking about?

292
00:19:05,680 --> 00:19:07,040
Keep your mouth shut.

293
00:19:10,240 --> 00:19:11,840
Why would he commit suicide?

294
00:19:11,840 --> 00:19:13,300
Why did he commit suicide?

295
00:19:13,400 --> 00:19:14,280
I don't know.

296
00:19:14,760 --> 00:19:17,280
Last night, after he left the room,

297
00:19:18,040 --> 00:19:19,440
I never saw him again.

298
00:19:22,240 --> 00:19:23,160
Miss Li.

299
00:19:25,720 --> 00:19:27,450
Then from last night until now,

300
00:19:28,160 --> 00:19:29,760
have you been anywhere else?

301
00:19:29,800 --> 00:19:30,600
No,

302
00:19:31,960 --> 00:19:33,490
I was in my room all the time.

303
00:19:33,960 --> 00:19:36,560
The madam of Yichun Brothel can testify for me.

304
00:19:39,040 --> 00:19:40,370
If you don't believe me,

305
00:19:40,760 --> 00:19:42,120
you can ask her.

306
00:19:51,600 --> 00:19:52,360
Xuanli,

307
00:19:52,760 --> 00:19:55,640
why did Niu Dali insist on having you serve him?

308
00:19:59,560 --> 00:20:00,760
As for this question,

309
00:20:02,520 --> 00:20:04,040
he can answer it for me.

310
00:20:13,600 --> 00:20:14,600
It's like this.

311
00:20:15,120 --> 00:20:16,880
Three years ago, I received a report.

312
00:20:16,880 --> 00:20:19,600
The informant said that at the Zhao residence in Lianhua Alley,

313
00:20:19,600 --> 00:20:22,720
a man was dragging an unconscious woman into the house.

314
00:20:23,280 --> 00:20:25,210
After hearing this, I rushed over.

315
00:20:25,680 --> 00:20:26,240
Officer,

316
00:20:26,480 --> 00:20:28,720
someone is raping a young woman.

317
00:20:29,000 --> 00:20:29,520
Hurry.

318
00:20:30,560 --> 00:20:31,490
Hurry, officer.

319
00:20:34,560 --> 00:20:35,220
Don't move.

320
00:20:36,800 --> 00:20:37,680
The man

321
00:20:37,760 --> 00:20:38,600
was Niu Dali.

322
00:20:39,240 --> 00:20:39,880
The woman.

323
00:20:44,640 --> 00:20:45,440
Afterward,

324
00:20:45,480 --> 00:20:48,080
Niu Dali was sentenced to three years for rape.

325
00:20:48,120 --> 00:20:50,580
He was just released from prison last month.

326
00:20:52,440 --> 00:20:53,170
At that time,

327
00:20:54,280 --> 00:20:55,960
I was still an innocent girl

328
00:20:56,360 --> 00:20:58,760
and hadn't been sold to Yichun Brothel yet.

329
00:20:58,880 --> 00:20:59,560
That night,

330
00:21:02,400 --> 00:21:03,720
I was alone at home.

331
00:21:40,960 --> 00:21:42,720
I was defiled by a scoundrel,

332
00:21:44,160 --> 00:21:46,090
which changed my destiny forever.

333
00:21:52,040 --> 00:21:52,880
Xuanli.

334
00:21:54,000 --> 00:21:56,600
So when Niu Dali went to Yichun Brothel for fun,

335
00:21:56,960 --> 00:21:58,360
he saw you at first glance

336
00:21:58,680 --> 00:22:00,210
and wanted you to serve him.

337
00:22:08,000 --> 00:22:09,040
Niu Dali...

338
00:22:10,320 --> 00:22:11,480
Is he really dead?

339
00:22:12,840 --> 00:22:13,640
Dead.

340
00:22:14,240 --> 00:22:15,600
Completely dead

341
00:22:16,400 --> 00:22:17,320
and cold.

342
00:22:24,200 --> 00:22:25,600
Look, here she comes.

343
00:22:25,800 --> 00:22:27,360
Where do you think she went?

344
00:22:27,520 --> 00:22:28,320
Who knows?

345
00:22:28,360 --> 00:22:29,690
She's been gone all day.

346
00:22:30,040 --> 00:22:32,800
I heard her client died yesterday.

347
00:22:33,280 --> 00:22:34,480
Why were you gone so long?

348
00:22:34,480 --> 00:22:35,480
I was worried sick.

349
00:22:35,480 --> 00:22:36,320
Are you okay?

350
00:22:37,120 --> 00:22:38,250
Don't worry, Madam.

351
00:22:38,680 --> 00:22:39,760
Xuanli is fine.

352
00:22:40,120 --> 00:22:41,640
Glad to hear it. Go on.

353
00:22:44,320 --> 00:22:45,520
Did she kill him?

354
00:22:46,000 --> 00:22:47,560
I didn't see her go out.

355
00:22:47,800 --> 00:22:48,880
Who knows?

356
00:22:48,920 --> 00:22:50,720
I think it most likely has something to do with her.

357
00:22:50,720 --> 00:22:52,200
What nonsense are you talking about?

358
00:22:52,200 --> 00:22:53,440
Too much free time, huh?

359
00:22:53,440 --> 00:22:54,760
Hurry up and entertain the guests.

360
00:22:54,760 --> 00:22:56,160
- If you don't have any, go find some.
- Yes.

361
00:22:56,160 --> 00:22:57,000
Go, go.

362
00:23:11,400 --> 00:23:12,330
Why are you here?

363
00:23:18,720 --> 00:23:20,200
Look at this pretty face.

364
00:23:21,200 --> 00:23:22,600
Hand over all your money.

365
00:23:24,080 --> 00:23:25,960
I saw everything you did.

366
00:23:30,800 --> 00:23:32,600
We've visited three liquor stalls.

367
00:23:32,600 --> 00:23:34,240
Do you have any leads?

368
00:23:35,160 --> 00:23:35,960
This morning,

369
00:23:36,080 --> 00:23:38,320
I smelled rice wine on Niu Dali's shoes.

370
00:23:38,600 --> 00:23:41,120
To make our customers lose their minds

371
00:23:41,160 --> 00:23:42,360
and spend extravagantly,

372
00:23:42,360 --> 00:23:44,360
Yichun Brothel only sells strong liquor,

373
00:23:44,360 --> 00:23:45,440
not rice wine.

374
00:23:47,040 --> 00:23:49,440
You mean on his way home,

375
00:23:49,520 --> 00:23:51,200
- he bought wine?
- Yes.

376
00:23:51,280 --> 00:23:52,440
Mellow rice wine,

377
00:23:52,480 --> 00:23:53,610
fragrant for miles.

378
00:23:53,840 --> 00:23:55,100
What about this stall?

379
00:23:56,400 --> 00:23:57,930
Sir, have a pot of rice wine.

380
00:24:04,640 --> 00:24:05,280
Good wine.

381
00:24:06,720 --> 00:24:07,360
Boss.

382
00:24:09,160 --> 00:24:11,080
Do you remember this man?

383
00:24:11,640 --> 00:24:13,500
Did he come to buy wine yesterday?

384
00:24:15,360 --> 00:24:16,360
I remember him.

385
00:24:16,720 --> 00:24:18,650
He came here to buy wine last night.

386
00:24:18,720 --> 00:24:20,720
Before leaving, he bumped into a traveler.

387
00:24:20,720 --> 00:24:22,720
The wine he just bought spilled all over the floor.

388
00:24:22,720 --> 00:24:24,440
The traveler apologized repeatedly.

389
00:24:24,440 --> 00:24:26,240
He bought another pot of wine from me

390
00:24:26,240 --> 00:24:27,920
and gave it to him as compensation.

391
00:24:27,920 --> 00:24:29,180
Is there any wine left?

392
00:24:31,560 --> 00:24:33,090
Boss, I'd like a pot of wine.

393
00:24:33,280 --> 00:24:34,210
Coming right up.

394
00:24:34,240 --> 00:24:35,280
The pot right in front

395
00:24:35,280 --> 00:24:36,540
was just filled today.

396
00:24:37,760 --> 00:24:38,620
Thank you, sir.

397
00:24:38,640 --> 00:24:39,760
Take care, sir.

398
00:24:45,360 --> 00:24:47,480
Niu Dali bought wine on his way home.

399
00:24:47,760 --> 00:24:49,490
The coin purse was still on him.

400
00:24:49,520 --> 00:24:52,720
The servant, Fan Le, said he went to Niu Dali's house to return the purse.

401
00:24:52,720 --> 00:24:54,920
That's how he found the body.

402
00:24:56,160 --> 00:24:57,360
He is lying.

403
00:26:06,720 --> 00:26:08,240
How are the notes coming along?

404
00:26:08,240 --> 00:26:09,240
Let me see.

405
00:26:11,920 --> 00:26:13,600
The victim's name is Fan Le.

406
00:26:14,360 --> 00:26:16,080
The proprietress of Yichun Brothel said

407
00:26:16,080 --> 00:26:18,400
he didn't return to the servant's quarters last night.

408
00:26:18,400 --> 00:26:20,660
He might have taken the chance to go home,

409
00:26:21,000 --> 00:26:22,260
and was murdered here.

410
00:26:24,640 --> 00:26:26,370
Let's go inside and take a look.

411
00:26:31,640 --> 00:26:33,080
Did you see him yesterday?

412
00:26:33,080 --> 00:26:35,160
I haven't seen anything recently.

413
00:26:35,280 --> 00:26:35,840
Okay.

414
00:26:36,680 --> 00:26:37,600
Then it's nothing.

415
00:26:37,600 --> 00:26:38,080
Okay.

416
00:26:38,440 --> 00:26:38,840
Come.

417
00:26:41,840 --> 00:26:43,360
There are stairs going up.

418
00:26:43,440 --> 00:26:45,360
One, two, three.

419
00:26:46,360 --> 00:26:47,020
Right side.

420
00:27:08,200 --> 00:27:09,060
What happened?

421
00:27:09,480 --> 00:27:12,480
Why is his cause of death exactly the same as Niu Dali's?

422
00:27:12,480 --> 00:27:14,040
His back was against the window.

423
00:27:14,040 --> 00:27:16,200
The wound on his neck is fatal.

424
00:27:16,440 --> 00:27:17,600
His right hand was clenching a razor,

425
00:27:17,600 --> 00:27:18,600
with blood on it.

426
00:27:21,600 --> 00:27:23,330
Judging from the rigor mortis,

427
00:27:23,560 --> 00:27:25,890
the time of death is less than eight hours.

428
00:27:26,000 --> 00:27:27,680
He also reeks of alcohol.

429
00:27:43,600 --> 00:27:44,200
Son,

430
00:27:45,120 --> 00:27:46,040
don't you think

431
00:27:46,080 --> 00:27:48,200
the MO of this case

432
00:27:48,240 --> 00:27:49,200
is very similar to a previous one?

433
00:27:49,200 --> 00:27:49,920
Right.

434
00:27:50,200 --> 00:27:52,530
Isn't that how Zhao Xuanli's father died?

435
00:27:53,080 --> 00:27:56,480
Niu Dali, Fan Le, and Zhao Xuanli's father all died like this.

436
00:27:56,640 --> 00:27:58,120
All had fatal wounds on the neck,

437
00:27:58,120 --> 00:27:59,760
sitting on the ground with their backs against the window.

438
00:27:59,760 --> 00:28:01,280
Wait. Such a crucial clue,

439
00:28:01,320 --> 00:28:03,600
why didn't you mention it at Niu Dali's crime scene?

440
00:28:03,600 --> 00:28:04,560
I forgot.

441
00:28:05,000 --> 00:28:06,800
I thought it was all a coincidence.

442
00:28:06,800 --> 00:28:08,480
But now seeing how Fan Le died,

443
00:28:08,560 --> 00:28:10,560
the MO should be the same.

444
00:28:11,000 --> 00:28:12,480
At the time of the incident,

445
00:28:12,480 --> 00:28:14,680
Zhao Xuanli's father was alone at home.

446
00:28:15,120 --> 00:28:17,920
According to the time of death inferred by the coroner,

447
00:28:17,920 --> 00:28:20,880
Zhao Xuanli has an alibi.

448
00:28:21,920 --> 00:28:24,680
So she should have an alibi this time too.

449
00:28:25,480 --> 00:28:27,520
These victims are all connected to her.

450
00:28:27,520 --> 00:28:29,600
I really don't know how she did it.

451
00:28:30,600 --> 00:28:31,720
It's sorcery.

452
00:28:38,000 --> 00:28:38,840
Sorcery

453
00:28:39,440 --> 00:28:40,680
can kill.

